get into the tub.

01:55.216 --> 01:57.518
Use this only
if you have to.
(whimpering)

01:57.551 --> 01:58.519
Take it.

02:13.934 --> 02:16.870
(footsteps in distance,
approaching)

02:29.783 --> 02:32.253
(gasping)

03:02.983 --> 03:06.487
Be on the lookout
for a homeless man
with active TB.

03:06.520 --> 03:07.888
