and contain him.

03:14.928 --> 03:18.699
Okay, Cooper and Sherman
are working in A43.

03:18.732 --> 03:21.535
Garcia and Montoya
are in A91.

03:21.569 --> 03:23.671
Becker's on the front desk.
Park, you're in U-2.

03:23.704 --> 03:24.938
