since last night,

06:30.090 --> 06:31.459
so we have a window.

06:31.459 --> 06:32.460
Okay, let's go.

06:32.493 --> 06:33.927
Give me a minute.

06:35.996 --> 06:38.966
Yeah, Russell Clarke's room.

06:38.999 --> 06:41.602
(phone ringing)

06:43.937 --> 06:46.574
