12:08.128 --> 12:09.329
Yeah.

12:09.362 --> 12:11.865
Ben.

12:11.899 --> 12:13.801
Thank you, Ben.

12:13.801 --> 12:15.502
Yeah.

12:18.171 --> 12:21.842
